<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFCapozzaLee.2C_Sohan1996">Capozza, Dennis R.; Lee, Sohan (1996). "Portfolio Characteristics and Net Asset Values in REITs". <i>The Canadian Journal of Economics / Revue canadienne d'Economique</i> <b>29</b> (Special Issue: Part 2): S520–S526. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F136100" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F136100" rel="nofollow">10.2307/136100</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Portfolio+Characteristics+and+Net+Asset+Values+in+REITs&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Canadian+Journal+of+Economics+%2F+Revue+canadienne+d%27Economique&amp;rft.aulast=Capozza&amp;rft.aufirst=Dennis+R.&amp;rft.au=Capozza%2C+Dennis+R.&amp;rft.au=Lee%2C+Sohan&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.volume=29&amp;rft.issue=Special+Issue%3A+Part+2&amp;rft.pages=S520%26ndash%3BS526&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F136100&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Herfindahl_index"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
