<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Herfindahl_index&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/public/testimony/hhi.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/public/testimony/hhi.htm" rel="nofollow">US Department of Justice example and market concentration cutoffs</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.unclaw.com/chin/teaching/antitrust/herfindahl.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.unclaw.com/chin/teaching/antitrust/herfindahl.htm" rel="nofollow">Herfindahl-Hirschman Index Calculator</a>. Web tool for calculating pre- and post-merger Herfindahl index.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/public/guidelines/horiz_book/hmg1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/public/guidelines/horiz_book/hmg1.html" rel="nofollow">Department of Justice and Federal Trade Commission Horizontal Merger Guidelines</a>. More detailed information about mergers, market concentration, and competition (from the <a href="/wiki/United_States_Department_of_Justice" title="United States Department of Justice">Department of Justice</a>).</li>
</ul>


